Variable ℱ:𝖦𝗋𝗈𝗎𝗉 provisionally

Theorem (GroupsCategories)
  Suppose
    ℱ:𝖦𝗋𝗈𝗎𝗉
  Then
    𝘊_ℱ:𝖢𝖺𝗍𝖾𝗀𝗈𝗋𝗒
  Proof
    [𝘊_ℱ] satisfies CategoryCompositionOfMorphisms by GroupCategoryCompositionOfMorphisms
    [𝘊_ℱ] satisfies CategoryCompositionIsAssociative by GroupCategoryCompositionIsAssociative
    [𝘊_ℱ] satisfies CategoryIdentityMorphisms by GroupCategoryIdentityMorphisms
  Therefore
    𝘊_ℱ:𝖢𝖺𝗍𝖾𝗀𝗈𝗋𝗒 by Categories
